      <!-- Left Column: Guidelines -->
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <h3 class="fw-bold mb-3">Effective Sleep Tips (Do's):</h3>
        <ol class="fs-5">
          <li><strong>Establish a Regular Sleep Schedule:</strong> Go to bed and wake up at the same time every day.</li>
          <li><strong>Create a Calming Bedtime Routine:</strong> Engage in relaxing activities like reading or meditation before sleep.</li>
          <li><strong>Optimize Your Sleep Environment:</strong> Ensure your room is dark, cool, and quiet.</li>
          <li><strong>Limit Screen Time:</strong> Avoid electronic devices at least one hour before bedtime.</li>
          <li><strong>Try Ayurvedic Remedies:</strong> Use warm milk with turmeric or herbal teas like chamomile to promote sleep.</li>
        </ol>
        <h3 class="fw-bold mt-4 mb-3">What Not To Do:</h3>
        <ul class="fs-5">
          <li>Do not consume caffeine or stimulants late in the day.</li>
          <li>Avoid heavy meals and vigorous exercise close to bedtime.</li>
          <li>Refrain from excessive screen time before sleep.</li>
          <li>Do not use alcohol as a sleep aid.</li>
        </ul>
